room_title: Escape room "Framed for Murder" by Immersion in Irvine
room_address: 1095 N Main St suite b Orange, CA 92867
room_description:
You have been tracking the whereabouts of an ancient relic known as the bloodstone. Following a lead, after lead, the elusive artifact cannot be found. During your search, a strain of murders has occurred, and you are now the prime suspect and have been wrongfully accused of foul play. 
You have hired a private investigator Rick Stacey to help find out who has set you up. Hoping he can help to clear your name and find out who the real killer is. Time is short, and Rick has contacted you, claiming he has the evidence needed to help exonerate you of this crime. 
Do you have what it takes to prove your innocence?
